      <title>黑石集团的 Zawadzki 认为私人信贷市场规模达 25 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/blackstone-s-zawadzki-sees-private-credit-as-25-trillion-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据该行业的巨头之一黑石集团称，规模达 1.7 万亿美元的私人借贷行业在扩张至 25 万亿美元的市场之前仍处于“练习阶段”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/blackstone-s-zawadzki-sees-private-credit-as-25-trillion-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 17:24:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
